"A buffer distance can be different for each feature within a vector layer."
msgstr "Una distancia buffer puede ser diferente para cada entidad de una capa vectorial."

#: ../../source/docs/gentle_gis_introduction/vector_spatial_analysis_buffers.rst:222
msgid ""
"Polygons can be buffered **inward** or **outward** from the polygon "
